                  , did make an assault, putting him in corporal fear and<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="176601160008"></xptr> danger of his life, and violently taking from his person one guinea, and 12 s. 6 d. in money numbered, his property
            </rs>, <rs id="t17660116-6-cd37" type="crimeDate">January 8, 1764</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17660116-6-off36 t17660116-6-cd37"></join>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17660116-6-off41 t17660116-6-cd37"></join>
