                     <interp inst="t17660116-6-person103" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I keep a public house, the Greyhound, in Red-cross-street, in the Greyhound Inn back gate in the Borough; the prisoner used my house for almost a year and a half, he always behaved well, and paid very honestly.</p>
               <p>Q. to prosecutor. How do you know you lost 1 l. 13 s. 6 d?</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. I lost more, but I chuse to swear to less.</p>
